<div class='media__message'>
<h4 class='h12 talk-link__speaker'>Chieko Asakawa</h4>
<h4 class='h9 m5'>
<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/chieko_asakawa_how_new_technology_helps_blind_people_explore_the_world?language=en' lang='en'>
How new technology helps blind people explore the world
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
Posted
<span class='meta__val'>
Dec 2015
</span>
</span>
<span class='meta__row'>
Rated
<span class='meta__val'>
Inspiring, Courageous
</span>
</span>
</div>
